text: Lots of anti-Mar sentiments in this link (and a couple-a cons for the rest plus some Duterte pros):  http://www.jamesparmis.net/ viral-why-i-am-voting-for-duterte-cayetano-a-christians-response-must-read/    It's an old link though, from the time LP hasn't explained the Yolanda funds.
